---
title: Cheesy Beyond Meat® and Rigatoni Bake with Veggies and Tomato Sauce
description: This loaded cheesy bake is packed with rigatoni pasta, a creamy tomato sauce and tender Beyond Meat®. It's a quick, delicious dinner that's sure to be a weeknight winner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/rigatonis-gratines-au-beyond-meat-c036d291.jpg
